{"tid":1072401,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"新90後感情9up食飯活動谷","createTime":"2019-03-22T04:01:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T19:16:31.000Z","uid":216724,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1332022ead342d75fca4303ed5ef10e30846b1a","tid":1072401,"uid":216724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"一個岩岩開既新谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家入黎傾計 打機 飯聚 唱K  踩單車 bbq  飲野  9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定期會有會有谷聚 只要你諗到既野都會有 你肯出黎一齊認識下新朋友就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地好得閒  一定會覆你<br />\n唔洗驚入到黎會講唔到野<br />\n感情事乜都可以講比我地聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴禁搵食厹娘娘5p仔   見到即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者report比谷主聽<br />\n<br />\n我地男女比例會平衡返<br />\n男嘅唔洗驚出到黎格劍<br />\n女嘅都唔洗驚出到黎得你一個女仔<br />\n未入到嘅巴打請耐心等候<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1DB2n6mA6XnmYy-5WSztXaoiXTDWFkJKJ6oOdSCyEuW4/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1DB2n6mA6XnmYy-5WSztXaoiXTDWFkJKJ6oOdSCyEuW4%2Fedit&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=fb4e70be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1DB2n6mA6XnmYy-5WSztXaoiXTDWFkJKJ6oOdSCyEuW4/edit</a><br />\n麻煩大家幫忙填一填方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d81dfb4262a92d44e924626ba801eddc0dbf2","tid":1072401,"uid":145383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:02:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c3b132ffe434dd66258b461aecb2d4cdf5e722","tid":1072401,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" cl